## How to install nix packages with home-manager + nix-system-graphics

# Install Nix
  https://nixos.org/download/

# Add/Restart nix-daemon service
  doas rc-service nix-daemon restart
  https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/User:Alxhr0/Nix_on_openrc

# Enable flakes and nix-command:
  echo "experimental-features = nix-command flakes" >> ~/.config/nix/nix.conf
  and to /etc/nix/nix.conf

# Cd to nix-home
  nix run github:nix-community/home-manager -- switch --flake .#lampis-home
  sudo -E env "PATH=$PATH" nix run 'github:numtide/system-manager' -- switch --flake .

## Done!!

=========================================================================================

## After:

# To update config/packages
  home-manager switch --flake .#lampis-home

# To clean up
  nix-collect-garbage -d   

# To update:
  nix flake update

# Generations/Rollback
  home-manager generations
  /nix/store/xxx-home-manager/generation/activate
